avirus: Three further deaths and six new cases confirmed in Ireland","permalink":"https:\/\/www.thejournal.ie\/covid-figures-update-5138639-Jul2020\/","stats":"<span class=\"red-views icon iconViewVeryPopular\"><\/span>46,298 Views","primary_tag":{"slug":"https:\/\/www.thejournal.ie\/figures\/news\/","name":"Figures"},"image":"<div id=\"read_next_banner\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.thejournal.ie\/covid-figures-update-5138639-Jul2020\/\"><img src=\"https:\/\/c0.thejournal.ie\/media\/2020\/07\/007-dept-of-health-2-290x120.jpg\"  id=\"r_n_image\" \/><\/a><\/div>","no_image":""}];

